{"tid":528531,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"干地都停火：我也鄙視摩佬","createTime":"2018-01-14T01:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T06:11:52.000Z","uid":333,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a0de02a2ccd03a34535ff68f61f9a6cf698dce33","tid":528531,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T01:48:31.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=ORkV3TibX6eVz69FFHa7AC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5840844c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】對於摩連奴日前表示鄙視自己，干地坦言自己也一樣，而且就對方的言論不會上心。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯領隊摩連奴（Jose Mourinho）跟車路士主帥干地（Antonio Conte）最近不停爆發口水戰，前者挪喻對方曾於意大利涉嫌打假波，而後者就批評摩佬是小人作為回應。<br />\n<br />\n摩佬於周五賽前記者會上坦言：「干地第1次侮辱我，我回應了，而且知道這個回應觸及一些令他受傷的事，之後他再侮辱我，但我改變了，只會鄙視他。對我來說，鄙視對方等於事情完結。」<br />\n<br />\n干地在周六帶領車路士主場賽和李斯特城0:0後，被問及此事時表示：「我認為，我會停止了。我也一樣鄙視他。我不知道他的說話，矛頭是不是我，但我沒有擔心，每天晚上都睡得很好。」<br />\n<br />\n據知，二人突然停火，是因為英格蘭足總及英格蘭足球聯賽領隊協會CEO比雲正密切留意今次的口水戰，所以曼聯及車路士都勸告他們終止今場口舌之爭。"},{"pid":"cb25f7eb18caf75fe408fc873db5ae07ea17c2f6","tid":528531,"uid":42820,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T03:30:03.000Z","msg":"執人口水尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524f475f1930ceac3a84555c780e552fa4c3a914","tid":528531,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T03:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4c0ce68939f3691a37ed44b4552573b2b7add9","tid":528531,"uid":109491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"走住嚟屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b441effc9b8a4430bf84aa1b35540e2a793056","tid":528531,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T03:52:02.000Z","msg":"小學雞嗌交咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de28437c9bb17a2cfc56dd8941b5aadb427af75","tid":528531,"uid":15486,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ed4c0ce68939f3691a37ed44b4552573b2b7add9","tid":528531,"uid":109491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"走住嚟屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T03:53:27.000Z","msg":"係摩佬走住黎屌下話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4179b9bccb22e2c8fd94fc148e09344e1994d4c","tid":528531,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T04:00:28.000Z","msg":"估下摩佬下個對手係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30af385a16497ef564ed22a18670d84b5aa3e0af","tid":528531,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T05:56:44.000Z","msg":"H!<br />\nH你老母！<br />\nH!<br />\nH!<br />\nH家族！"},{"pid":"082a294a534607875d02a443f6301ca3eaccb730","tid":528531,"uid":33730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4179b9bccb22e2c8fd94fc148e09344e1994d4c","tid":528531,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T04:00:28.000Z","msg":"估下摩佬下個對手係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:00:52.000Z","msg":"仲有人理條煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450faa964257c48089be4b69636a331ab8077cbb","tid":528531,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:02:52.000Z","msg":"metoo"},{"pid":"4ecaf81dae1d0bcaa2b56a96c90ae714f635bbb0","tid":528531,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:11:52.000Z","msg":"和波咪走住黎屌"}]}